/a>User Based Metrics (Digital Products)</h1>\n<p>see also <a href=\"/PublicPersonalKnowledgeBase/notes/c7rsts0s84pjnj28m21ee3s#^companygoals\">Product School Book</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"impressions\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#impressions\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Impressions</h1>\n<h1 id=\"ctr-\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#ctr-\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"block-anchor anchor-heading\" id=\"^ctr\" href=\"#^ctr\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>CTR </h1>\n<h1 id=\"task-success--\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#task-success--\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"block-anchor anchor-heading\" id=\"^task_success\" href=\"#^task_success\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Task Success  </h1>\n<p>Dwell time, not </p>\n<h1 id=\"active-users-\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#active-users-\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"block-anchor anchor-heading\" id=\"^active-users\" href=\"#^active-users\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Active Users </h1>\n<h2 id=\"daily\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#daily\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Daily</h2>\n<h2 id=\"monthly\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#monthly\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Monthly</h2>\n<h1 id=\"depth-of-scroll\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#depth-of-scroll\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Depth Of scroll</h1>\n<h1 id=\"user-stickiness\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#user-stickiness\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>User Stickiness</h1>\n<h1 id=\"user-engagement-\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#user-engagement-\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"block-anchor anchor-heading\" id=\"^engagement\" href=\"#^engagement\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>User Engagement </h1>\n<h1 id=\"user-feedback\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#user-feedback\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>User Feedback</h1>\n<h1 id=\"metrics-for-non-continuous-use\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#metrics-for-non-continuous-use\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Metrics for non-continuous use</h1>\n<h1 id=\"jobs-partner-findingsearch\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#jobs-partner-findingsearch\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Jobs/ Partner finding/Search</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Users will use linkedin less/none if they find a job</li>\n<li>Users will use facebook dating less/nont if they find a partner</li>\n<li>If search is <strong>not</strong> successful, users will come back to search page and try another link/query.</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"user-engagement-task-completion-etc\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#user-engagement-task-completion-etc\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>User Engagement, task completion etc</h1>\n<p></p><p></p><div class=\"portal-container\">\n<div class=\"portal-head\">\n<div class=\"portal-backlink\">\n<div class=\"portal-title\">From <span class=\"portal-text-title\">UX Research and KPI's</span></div>\n<a href=\"/PublicPersonalKnowledgeBase/notes/Xt3jxOCtXrIuY4ANViyoK\" class=\"portal-arrow\">Go to text <span class=\"right-arrow\">→</span></a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"portal-parent-anchor\" class=\"portal-parent\" markdown=\"1\">\n<div class=\"portal-parent-fader-top\"></div>\n<div class=\"portal-parent-fader-bottom\"></div><p><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"block-anchor anchor-heading\" id=\"^heart\" href=\"#^heart\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a><a href=\"https://static.googleusercontent.com/media/research.google.com/en//pubs/archive/36299.pdf\">HEART framework by Google</a>. </p>\n</div></div><p></p><p></p>\n<h1 id=\"explicit-user-feedback-on-recommendations-\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#explicit-user-feedback-on-recommendations-\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"block-anchor anchor-heading\" id=\"^user-feedback-recommendations\" href=\"#^user-feedback-recommendations\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Explicit User feedback on Recommendations </h1>\n<ul>\n<li>clicks (<a title=\"Private\" style=\"color: brown\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\">^engagement (Private)</a></li>\n<li>likes/hearths/etc </li>\n<li>report</li>\n<li>Time spend</li>\n<li>impression time</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/PublicPersonalKnowledgeBase/notes/JClhWanv6nT58jkwQvo3o\">AB Testing</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/PublicPersonalKnowledgeBase/notes/v4bhymavtwv0dpnzw0klwwa\">Search Ranking</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"wn8PE1RhG0znK1alrGFYv","title":"Root","d